Title: Between the lines
DateModified: '2019-03-09'
DatePublished: '2019-03-09'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2019/applications/between-the-lines
SetInCountry: Libya
Category: I didn't expect to find
AuthorName: Seham Ferjani
AuthorCountry: Tunisia
Text: "The sense of adventure, possibilities, frequency, fear, adrenaline, and all\
  \ that drives the heart to pulse quickly and sense of it existence in the chest\
  \ is what I aspire to  . \nOne day I started a trip were not considered , I did\
  \ not plan for  passionately as usual , adventure I did not knock her door by my\
  \ own will, but I was leaving an  adventure was lived by more than a million people\
  \ ... The revolution of a people on a dictatorial regime, so how can this not be\
  \ the biggest adventure ? but i was forced to withdraw from it \u060C fear has my\
  \ father's heart  and decided to start a trip across the border . I convinced myself\
  \ that there are adventures and things to discover on this journey, new life and\
  \ obstacles .. \nLeaving my country was difficult but I kind of going to my second\
  \ country too , I belong to a family which the father Libyan and the mother tunisian,\
  \  yes I'm half blood like it calls , lol ."
